labels.privacy label detail: A simple uniform random 1% subsample of the target data.   It provides limited privacy by redacting records at random, allowing survey takers to deny that their information was included in the public release.
labels.features list: PUMA, AGEP, SEX, MSP, HISP, RAC1P, NOC, NPF, OWN_RENT, PINCP_DECILE, POVPIP
